00:06:07.950 --> 00:06:11.550
And what Firebase is is
both a client-side SDK

00:06:11.550 --> 00:06:13.770
and a bunch of cloud services.

00:06:13.770 --> 00:06:17.040
These cloud services are
a bunch of things we host

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:17.740
and we control.

00:06:17.740 --> 00:06:21.150
So if you're familiar with
other cloud providers,

00:06:21.150 --> 00:06:23.700
you may be just thinking, all
right, I go into the cloud,

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:25.174
and I spin up a VM.

00:06:25.174 --> 00:06:27.090
And then I still have
