00:06:27.090 --> 00:06:29.970
to expose this
service to my user,

00:06:29.970 --> 00:06:32.250
to my client in
a reasonable way.

00:06:32.250 --> 00:06:33.780
Firebase isn't like that.

00:06:33.780 --> 00:06:37.590
There's a ton of things on
that graph that everyone needs.

00:06:37.590 --> 00:06:38.970
Everyone needs authentication.

00:06:38.970 --> 00:06:41.190
There are very, very
few apps in the world

00:06:41.190 --> 00:06:43.060
that don't log in a user.

00:06:43.060 --> 00:06:45.510
And so the fact that
