00:06:45.510 --> 00:06:48.985
are rewriting authentication
code just doesn't make sense.

00:06:48.985 --> 00:06:50.360
You have to worry
about security.

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:53.220
You have to worry about all
of these little facets that

00:06:53.220 --> 00:06:55.350
just waste your time.

00:06:55.350 --> 00:06:57.450
And I'll come back
